From 4a8f65cf3f4c486ce91196d221410a7dc835dc56 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Keanu Czirjak <keanu.czirjak@arm.com>
Date: Tue, 31 Mar 2026 12:02:24 +0100
Subject: [LOW RISK] [CI] add missing GPU_IMAGE var for manylinux2_28_aarch64-builder CUDA case

This commit adds the GPU_IMAGE var to fix the manylinux2_28_aarch64-builder:cuda* image build errors in CI.
This is because the build.sh script uses 'set -u' (nounset), hence GPU_IMAGE must be set.

Self-assessment: LOW RISK
      1. Do you have any doubt about letting this patch go outside Arm, or do you think others in the team might? No
      2. Is the patch based on a previously IP approved patch with trivial changes? No
      3. Are all changes in this patch either written by yourself or copy-pasted from the same project? Yes
      4. Is the contribution in Arm’s commercial Interest? Yes
      5. Is this the first time that Arm has made a significant modification to any of the files changed in this patch or does it add a new file? No
      6. Does this patch disclose anything that is not the public knowledge? No
      7. Does the patch mention any company name other than Arm? No
      8. Does the patch contain any inappropriate use of trademarks? No
      9. Does the patch contribute beyond the scope that has been approved? No
      10. Does the patch contain a patentable idea for which a patent has not yet been filed? No
      11. Does the patch disclose any aspects of micro-architecture of any Arm HW IP? No
      12. Does the patch use HW architecture features not previously used in the project? No
      13. Does the patch contain generative AI output? No
---
 .ci/docker/manywheel/build.sh | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/.ci/docker/manywheel/build.sh b/.ci/docker/manywheel/build.sh
index ea05ae30b91..57029edbc26 100755
--- a/.ci/docker/manywheel/build.sh
+++ b/.ci/docker/manywheel/build.sh
@@ -76,6 +76,7 @@ case ${image} in
         ;;
     manylinux2_28_aarch64-builder:cuda*)
         TARGET=cuda_final
+        GPU_IMAGE=arm64v8/almalinux:8
         DOCKER_GPU_BUILD_ARG="--build-arg BASE_CUDA_VERSION=${GPU_ARCH_VERSION} --build-arg DEVTOOLSET_VERSION=13"
         DOCKERFILE_SUFFIX="_cuda_aarch64"
         ;;
